Package org.group8.simulator.model

Class SimulationResults

java.lang.Object
org.group8.simulator.model.SimulationResults
@Entity public class SimulationResults extends Object
The SimulationResults class represents the results of a simulation run. It stores various metrics such as average time, probabilities, times spent at different service points, and utilization rates for each service point. This class is mapped to the "simulation_results" table in the database.

  • Constructor Details

    • SimulationResults

      public SimulationResults(double averageTime, int totalPatients, int completedVisits, double labProbability, double xrayProbability, double treatmentProbability, double arrivalTime, double checkInTime, double doctorTime, double labTime, double xrayTime, double treatmentTime, double endTime, double checkInUtilization, double doctorUtilization, double labUtilization, double xrayUtilization, double treatmentUtilization)
      Constructs a SimulationResults object with all the necessary metrics for a simulation run, including utilization rates.
      Parameters:
      averageTime - the average time spent by patients
      totalPatients - the total number of patients
      completedVisits - the number of patients who completed their visits
      labProbability - the probability of being referred to the lab
      xrayProbability - the probability of being referred to x-ray
      treatmentProbability - the probability of being referred to treatment
      arrivalTime - the average arrival time
      checkInTime - the time spent at check-in
      doctorTime - the time spent with the doctor
      labTime - the time spent in the lab
      xrayTime - the time spent in x-ray
      treatmentTime - the time spent in treatment
      endTime - the total simulation end time
      checkInUtilization - the utilization rate of the check-in service point
      doctorUtilization - the utilization rate of the doctor service point
      labUtilization - the utilization rate of the lab service point
      xrayUtilization - the utilization rate of the x-ray service point
      treatmentUtilization - the utilization rate of the treatment service point
